Java Date & Time API
Pehle Problem Kya Thi?

Java 8 se pehle hum use karte the:

Date
Calendar
SimpleDateFormat

Inme problems thi:

😵 Difficult API
❌ Mutable (value change ho sakti thi)
❌ Thread-safe nahi thi
❌ Date calculations mushkil the

Isliye Java 8 me ek naya package introduce hua:
java.time


Interview Questions ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
Q1. Java 8 se pehle kaunsi classes use hoti thi?

Answer

Date
Calendar
SimpleDateFormat
Q2. LocalDate.now() kya return karta hai?

Answer

Current Date
Q3. LocalTime.now() kya return karta hai?

Answer

Current Time
Q4. LocalDateTime.now() kya return karta hai?

Answer

Current Date + Current Time
Q5. LocalDate immutable hai?

Answer

Yes
